4. NiFi RemoteShellCommands - user values embedded into SSH command strings passed to sh -c
5. NiFi Registry ShellRunner (line 60) - same sink pattern as NiFi
6. NiFi Registry NssShellCommands - same command building pattern
7. NiFi Registry OsxShellCommands - same macOS command building pattern

The ShellUserGroupProvider.getDelayProperty/getTimeoutProperty findings from Query 2 were determined to be false positives - these configuration values only appear in error messages, never in shell commands.

